Class BufferedObservationSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opengis.gml.v32.impl.AbstractGMLImpl
      • net.opengis.gml.v32.impl.AbstractFeatureImpl
        • org.vast.ogc.gml.GenericFeatureImpl
          • org.vast.ogc.om.BufferedObservationSeries
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractFeature, AbstractGML, IDataConsumer, IDataProvider, GenericFeature, IObservationSeries, ISweInputDataStream, ISweOutputDataStream

    public class BufferedObservationSeries
extends GenericFeatureImpl
implements IObservationSeries

    Implementation of IObservationSeries whose data is stored entirely in memory and is fully mutable. Data is stored internally using a DataList object.

    Since:
    Aug 20, 2012
    Author:
    Alex Robin
